-- Turkey's Albaraka bank mandates banks for maximum $500 mln sukuk issue
-- By Ece Toksabay
-- Thu May 08, 2014 04:31AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, May 8 (Reuters) - Turkish participation bank Albaraka <ALBRK.IS>, owned by Bahrain-based Islamic lender Al Baraka, mandated banks for a sukuk issue worth maximum $500 million, it said on Thursday.

